"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"The University of California at Berkeley recently [added](https://defi-learning.org/) a massively open online course, or MOOC, on decentralized finance to its Fall 2021 semester offering.\\n\\nDawn Song, a professor of electrical engineering and computer science at UC Berkeley and founder of blockchain platform Oasis Network, told Cointelegraph that she will help lead the DeFi course, alongside professors from Stanford and Imperial College London. According to Song, DeFi is becoming a fundamentally new way to build financial infrastructure, which is why it’s important for students everywhere to learn about the topic:\\n\\n> “About 300 computer science and finance students have signed up for the course, yet given the enormous interest of DeFi, we are also offering a MOOC version open to everyone globally. In total, over 1400 students have signed up for Berkeley’s DeFi course.”\\n\\nSong mentioned that UC Berkeley previously offered a shorter, more experimental DeFi course during its Spring 2021 semester. She explained that due to the success and interest of that class, the university is now offering a full semester course covering the most important concepts in DeFi.\",\"timestamp\":1639035526,\"title\":\"Where you can learn about DeFi\"},\"digest\":\"8V-yKS7Wz-TkbX46TPD3UXaR9HobuCW2diLhackeCuI\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x9E1eD0a565710397B9d0Fb0716dCBe1eC41fdbD8\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"asy-zcQvgN0cJLMxowtbM4LMgZXODdDCEkaL1RjpDOU\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"mdLxHFn7OH7SBvCz14LlvPuk-muQb8S5LSrou0ogAx0\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"RnAcUj6SiftgD9vAE_2iMZTBHo8FSStZvYZ-laXNMuebW6hajxmJpOwvpgQSYLfxBSskirMuga3d6zyK4-C6sA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xd42bfa31586071b855020eee8b2b467cbdb1c1f0f118b44ac3935178c9531cc6635d20aed89ab8714a5d9c916f0dfccb3a134661a72182d5527a7d5ce10978ca1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"asy-zcQvgN0cJLMxowtbM4LMgZXODdDCEkaL1RjpDOU\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"mdLxHFn7OH7SBvCz14LlvPuk-muQb8S5LSrou0ogAx0\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"8V-yKS7Wz-TkbX46TPD3UXaR9HobuCW2diLhackeCuI\"}"